<section class="spaced what-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow"><span class="blue-dot"></span>Honest</span>
      <h2><span class="primary-blue">A working ledger.</span> <span class="accent">Not your accountant's tool</span></h2>
      <p>We made this for the people who keep track on a notepad. Not for the office.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="what-grid">
      <div class="what-col">
        <h3>What it is</h3>
        <ul class="what-list">
          <li>
            <span class="what-bullet">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
            </span>
            <span>The notepad you keep in your head, on your phone instead</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="what-bullet">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
            </span>
            <span>A clear list of who owes you and who you owe</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="what-bullet">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
            </span>
            <span>One inbox for every invoice, organized by person</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="what-bullet">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
            </span>
            <span>Yours forever — export everything, anytime, in any format</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="what-bullet">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
            </span>
            <span>Free for crews up to 10 people</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="what-col">
        <h3>What it isn't</h3>
        <ul class="what-list">
          <li>
            <span class="what-bullet what-bullet-neutral">·</span>
            <span>Not accounting software (no ledger, no journal, no GAAP)</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="what-bullet what-bullet-neutral">·</span>
            <span>Not a way to skip the books — at month end, send a clean package to your accountant</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="what-bullet what-bullet-neutral">·</span>
            <span>Not a payment processor — we don't move money, we track it</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="what-bullet what-bullet-neutral">·</span>
            <span>Not a tax tool — talk to a professional for that</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="what-bullet what-bullet-neutral">·</span>
            <span>Not a subscription trap — leave anytime with all your data</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
